Class Word

  • java.lang.Object
    • Word

  • public class Word
extends java.lang.Object
    Project 1 This class represents each word used in the WordGUI. The word size is 3 and it holds the wordstring. This class also contains 1 constructor and 3 methods, 2 of the three being an override from the Object class. The constructors sets the wordstring, isValidWord method checks if a string is a valid word, the toString returns the wordstring, and the compareTo compares two words based on the wordstring.
